<div id="pf63" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="63"><div class="pc pc63 w0 h0"><div class="t m0 x9 h5 yb ff13 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls9 ws0">98 <span class="ff4 fs0 ls0">  上海交通大学问答 </span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h6 y20 ff6 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">看书也偏重看古人的书。希望大家也多了解一些传统文化，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2b ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">从老祖宗的智慧中汲取营养。 </div><div class="t m0 x9 ha y233 ffa fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">主持人结语： </div><div class="t m0 x1b hb y234 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">诚如堪布刚才所言，<span class="_ _7"></span>传统文化博大精深，<span class="_ _7"></span>因此，<span class="_ _7"></span>如果我</div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y235 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 lsb ws0">们能将儒释道甚至中西方文化融会贯<span class="lsc">通，智慧就会比较成</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y236 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">熟，看问题也会更客观。 </div><div class="t m0 x1b hb y237 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">听了堪布的讲座，<span class="_ _9"></span>我有一个深刻的感悟：<span class="_ _9"></span>人生的每分每</div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y238 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">秒都是有意义的，<span class="_ _9"></span>任何一个善念或者恶念都会起作用，<span class="_ _9"></span>对今</div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y239 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">生或者来世都会产生影响。<span class="_ _9"></span>有些朋友算过命，<span class="_ _9"></span>觉得自己一生</div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y23a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">就这样了。<span class="_ _7"></span>我想劝这些人：<span class="_ _7"></span>命是可以改的，<span class="_ _7"></span>如果自己不断地</div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y23b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">行善，不断地利益众生，一定会走上幸福之路。 </div><div class="t m0 x1b hb y23c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">好，<span class="_ _7"></span>请大家全体起立，<span class="_ _7"></span>以热烈的掌声感谢堪布、<span class="_ _7"></span>欢送堪</div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y23d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">布！ </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
